						<div class="postbody">Having IRQ pointing at an RTI will generally work. But in the NMI handler, you'll usually want to set a variable to notify the main program that a <span class="posthilit">vertical</span> blank has begun. So that I don't have to push and pull A, I just have it do <strong>inc nmis</strong>.</div>

